---
title: Sun-Dried Tomato Meatloaves with Onion Couscous & Roasted Green Beans & Zucchini
description: These meatloaves are not your mother’s meatloaves (or maybe they are? We don’t know your mom). For one, they’re baked on a sheet pan, which means more craggy edges for crisping and browning than a loaf pan. They’re also filled with chewy bits of sun-dried tomato that burst with tangy, savory flavor. And lastly, they’re smothered in a creamy onion sauce. Thoughts, Mom? Vegetables you say? The meatloaves are accompanied by roasted carrots and zucchini, plus buttery, garlicky couscous.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66955e74b0a47382be8702f8-6642077c.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6698179da33da88d87990500-en-US.pdf
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sun-dried-tomato-meatloaves-6698179da33da88d87990500
cuisine: North America
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 850 kcal
